Growers will now take home Sh4,040 per tonne from the current Sh3,700.Millers face Sh500,000 if caught underpaying farmers. Sugarcane farmers will from tomorrow earn more for their sweat after the Sugar Cane Pricing Committee increased the price of the raw material by eight percent. 



